209.7	Yoga	Yoga	Yoga is a physical, mental, and spiritual discipline, originating in ancient India. The goal of yoga, or of the person practicing yoga, is the attainment of a state of perfect spiritual insight and tranquility while meditating on the Hindu concept of divinity or Brahman. The word is associated with meditative practices in Hinduism, Jainism, and Buddhism.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/01/Shiva_Bangalore_.jpg/220px-Shiva_Bangalore_.jpg
